{"tid":539144,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇試過自信地打 J ?","createTime":"2018-01-24T10:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T15:52:49.000Z","uid":123335,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"61e3d2ccf537469e96b1a4effeeedde1d28786ad","tid":539144,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"方法係將 Psychology 中既 Power posing , 結合打J , <br />\n目的使男人以最佳姿勢，享受打 J  既過程，<br />\n提升男性既福祉, 將打J 快樂度最大化 <br />\n<br />\nPower posing 打J 法，係有科學根據 (Amy Cuddy, 2010) <br />\n<br />\n研究顯示, <br />\n使用power posing , <br />\n人類既皮質醇(Cortisol) 會下降 25% , 相反用自卑姿勢 , 則上升15% <br />\n皮質醇的下降, 會使打J時更加放鬆 , 更能專注AV 當中, 更加投入<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/173844_7ba64e1c268d88cf24c5e6e63f7449a3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F173844_7ba64e1c268d88cf24c5e6e63f7449a3.png&h=da246b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外, 研究顯示<br />\n使用power posing , <br />\n人類既睪固酮(Testosterone) 會上升20% , 相反用自卑姿勢 ，則下降10% <br />\n睪固酮的提升 , 能使男人以最雄性, 最威武既一面, 霸氣地打J ！<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/174400_d0021272bf0955571b8686048f90fc38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F24%2F174400_d0021272bf0955571b8686048f90fc38.png&h=a3075be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於點樣自信地使用Power posing 打J ? <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以參考下圖: <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> 正確的Power posing： </strong></span><img src=\"http://www.i2clipart.com/cliparts/9/3/a/f/clipart-green-tick-93af.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.i2clipart.com%2Fcliparts%2F9%2F3%2Fa%2Ff%2Fclipart-green-tick-93af.png&h=b2cafb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/24/175126_9161c736d5922e86c690a3387bf0fc7e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?